{
 "name": "RPlog_Reunion_and_Redirection",
 "title": "Reunion and Redirection",
 "summary": "At the Union Starport on Caspar, the dark adept Simon Sezirok, the eccentric Mira, and the Jedi student Markus regroup after a chaotic incident, drawing the cold attention of Ambassador Dises and his guards. Mira, irrepressibly proud of her speed in dodging a 'fire-bean,' brushes off the fuss while Simon quietly manages the situation he defused. As the wary Ambassador presses for details about who attacked, the group navigates the awkward aftermath and considers their next move, the reunion redirecting their fractured path forward.",
